item.title: CVE-2023-22303|2024-08-02T10:07:05.970Z -- tp-link -- tp-link%20sg105pe
item.description: TP-Link SG105PE firmware prior to 'TL-SG105PE(UN) 1.0_1.0.0 Build 20221208' contains an authentication bypass vulnerability. Under the certain conditions, an attacker may impersonate an administrator of the product. As a result, information may be obtained and/or the product's settings may be altered with the privilege of the administrator.
